<div id="pf4414" class="pf w4e h2fe" data-page-no="4414"><div class="pc pc4414 w4e h2fe"><div class="t m552 x62 h33 y2f7f ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 12 June 17-23 </div><div class="t m217c x92 h33 y23b8 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Ye shall have a song, as in the </div><div class="t ma9b x0 h33 y23a3 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">night when a holy solemnity is kept; </div><div class="t m28d3 x0 h33 y44f ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and gladness of heart, as when one </div><div class="t m1adb x0 h33 y32d ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">goeth with a pipe to come into the </div><div class="t m1a44 x0 h33 y5f5 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mountain of the Lord, to the mighty </div><div class="t m9a6 x0 h33 y1b52 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">One of Israel. And the Lord shall </div><div class="t m22bc x0 h33 y1033 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cause his glorious voice to be heard, </div><div class="t m1634 x0 h33 y20a ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and shall shew the lighting down </div><div class="t m1711 x0 h33 y15c7 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of his arm, with the indignation of </div><div class="t m1ac4 x0 h33 y1ba4 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">his anger, and with the flame of a </div><div class="t m237 x0 h33 y173 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">devouring fire, with scattering, and </div><div class="t mcee x0 h33 y195 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tempest, and hailstones&quot; (Isa. </div><div class="t m6ce x0 h33 y51 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">30:29, 30). </div><div class="t m976 x92 h35 ye74 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">As a climax to the supernatural </div><div class="t mdcd xc4 h35 y436 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">intervention of heaven in the affairs of </div><div class="t m30a x0 h35 y29e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">this sinful world, the King of kings and </div><div class="t m3b3 x0 h35 ydb ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lord of lords appears in His glorious </div><div class="t m8b8 x0 h35 y8d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">second coming. </div><div class="t m83c x92 h35 y363 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In this lesson we will review some </div><div class="t m116 x0 h35 y214 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the dramatic events that take place </div><div class="t m194 x0 h35 y206b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">immediately before the second </div><div class="t m9d3 x0 h35 y147f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">coming of Jesus. </div><div class="t m272 x92 h35 y405 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The reason for this study is, </div><div class="t mb84 x0 h35 ycbe ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">naturally, to have as exact an idea </div><div class="t m6fe x0 h35 y450 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as possible of the magnitude and the </div><div class="t mb0 x0 h35 y41c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sequence of these phenomena, as </div><div class="t m435 x0 h35 y64 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">appear evident from the analysis of </div><div class="t m993 x0 h35 y2c0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Bible texts and of the spirit of </div><div class="t m6d5 x0 h35 y43d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prophecy writings. And let us say, by </div><div class="t mdcb x0 h35 y5d7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the way, that we have tried to include </div><div class="t maa4 x0 h35 y26e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">this week as many quotations from </div><div class="t m70e x0 h35 y97 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ellen G. White&apos;s writings as possible, </div><div class="t m864 x0 h35 y305 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">since the servant of the Lord saw all </div><div class="t m3b9 x0 h35 y5c6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">those appalling scenes and was </div><div class="t m7ce x0 h35 yeb ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">overwhelmed by a clear vision of the </div><div class="t m6e9 xb7 h35 yae9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">reality. This is why she was in a </div><div class="t m8a5 x0 h35 y1a9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">position to write with accuracy and </div><div class="t m8e1 x0 h35 y713 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">knowledge, enlarging on the brief </div><div class="t ma42 xb7 h35 y165 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">statements and descriptions that we </div><div class="t m150 xb7 h35 y8a9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">find in the Word of God. </div><div class="t m3c2 x15 h35 y13e0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What we really need, though, is not </div><div class="t m862 xb7 h35 y411 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">only a theoretical knowledge of these </div><div class="t m19 xb7 h35 yc8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">majestic happenings, but a </div><div class="t m3ed xb7 h35 y2027 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">reassurance of the absolute certainty </div><div class="t m7ed xb7 h35 y225 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the prophecies and promises of </div><div class="t m982 xb7 h35 y2037 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God for this great hour. We need to </div><div class="t m5f8 xb7 h35 yfe5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">develop and strengthen our faith  </div><div class="t m6de x1c h35 y23b0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">during these times of comparative </div><div class="t mbd8 x1c h35 y2314 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">calm and serenity so that when the </div><div class="t m422 x1c h35 y1585 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">great day of God comes, we may keep </div><div class="t maa2 x1c h35 ya5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our confidence in the One who never </div><div class="t m1c5 x1c h35 yf4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fails and is exceedingly powerful and </div><div class="t mb6c x1c h35 y50c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">capable of giving us much more than </div><div class="t m977 x1c h35 y25a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">we can ask or think. </div><div class="t m3c2 x56 h35 y190 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">When by the grace of God we shall </div><div class="t m823 x1c h35 y4c9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">see Jesus riding on clouds of glory </div><div class="t m2a8 x1c h35 y1c9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and accompanied by all His holy </div><div class="t m11b x1c h35 y620 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">angels, all our past afflictions will </div><div class="t m2f0 x1c h35 y2b3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">look insignificant. When we approach </div><div class="t m62b x1c h35 y1217 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the pearly gates of the New Jerusalem, </div><div class="t m1480 x1c h35 y54 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">led by the great Captain of our </div><div class="t mae1 x1c h35 yae7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">salvation, we will praise Him who is </div><div class="t m710 x1c h35 ya55 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our victory. We will give Him all the </div><div class="t m152 x1c h35 y6c0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">honor and the glory, because with His </div><div class="t mae1 x1c h35 yb3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">inspiring life and His vicarious death </div><div class="t mac8 x1c h35 y612 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He saved us, forgiving our sins and </div><div class="t m11f x1c h35 yff ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">transforming our character for </div><div class="t ma61 x1c h35 y55b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">heaven. </div><div class="t mf7 x5a h33 y357 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m2c9 x5a h33 y9e8 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m6cb x86 h33 y6f4 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A Partial Resurrection </div><div class="t m1cb0 x86 h33 yd34 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Dan. 12:2; Rev. 1:7) </div><div class="t m119f x5a h33 y326 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m592 xae h33 y325 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Two Groups </div><div class="t mded x86 h33 yba5 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Ps. 46:1-3) </div><div class="t m3ce x5a h33 y2ac ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m1b8c xae h33 y2ac ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Glorious Second Coming </div><div class="t m7c x58 h33 y1e4 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">â€¢ </div><div class="t m1928 x86 h33 y42b ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Matt. 24:</div><div class="t m874 xa2 h35 y9f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">27) </div><div class="t mb06 x5a h33 y411 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t mcf0 x86 h33 y343 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Four Great Events </div><div class="t mc43 x86 h33 y115 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Isa. 25:8, 9) </div><div class="t mb06 x5a h33 y188 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t me9d x86 h33 yc9 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Toward the Pearly Gates </div><div class="t m1a3a x86 h33 y884 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 1:5, 6) </div><div class="t me5d x5a h33 y2f5 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m1fef x86 h33 y2f5 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How to Make Sure of Our </div><div class="t m114b x86 h33 y35c ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Participation (Rev. 12:11) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
